{"tid":1044513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警大埔駕電單車撞欄 送院不治","createTime":"2019-03-03T03:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T03:28:25.000Z","uid":51620,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd52abcf6b42fc6aba63d7d43b20f2cee04e0bd","tid":1044513,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190303/59323955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59323955&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=eb710b1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59323955&h=bbc4053d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190303/59323955</a><br />\n<br />\n【06:00】死者是一名休班警員<br />\n【01:18】司機送院搶救不治<br />\n<br />\n大埔太和路支路發生致命車禍，昨晚約11時42分，一名33歲男子，駕駛本田CB1000R大馬力電單車，沿太和路往吐露港公路上水方向行駛，其間在一個上斜右彎失控，「波勾」撞向左邊鐵欄，電單車衝前10多米才停下，司機拋出車外，頭部重創昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，死者是一名休班警員，事發時有其他駕駛人士經過，見狀立即停車報警及協助救援。救護員到場將傷者送大埔那打素醫院搶救，惜延至零時28分不治。警方將出事電單車拖返大欖涌車輛檢驗中心。<br />\n新界北總區交通部特別調查隊正跟進調查案件。任何人如目睹意外發生或有任何資料提供，請致電3661 3800與調查人員聯絡。"},{"pid":"10e1774c9fe44824a2dfd1a5a5d9ef296ce00e4e","tid":1044513,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"707262894ddfb8a750fb8d0d5e7af9e77b52136c","tid":1044513,"uid":171409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"生死有命 做差佬就預左"}]}